          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Sale price. Data provided by the owner of the factory. Price given as  0.0238 USD/kg for 2022. The prices were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2023-06-01) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="a9358458-9724-4f03-b622-106eda248916" amount="0.0" unitId="577e242a-461f-44a7-922c-d8e1c3d2bf45">
          <name xml:lang="en">water content</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">dimensionless</unitName>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="6d9e1462-80e3-4f10-b3f4-71febd6f1168" amount="0.0" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">water in wet mass</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="67f102e2-9cb6-4d20-aa16-bf74d8a03326" amount="1.0" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">wet mass</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. The production volume is based on the production volume of clay roof tiles in Europe (RER dataset) and the nominal GDP 2019 for EC and Europe. It's assumed the same share between glazed and conventional clay roof tiles.
According to EuroStat, the production of clay roofing tiles in the European Union in 2019 was 2'577'423'791 units [1]. In Europe the assumed average weight per unit is 4 kg [2]. The nominal (current) GDP of the EU in 2019 was 15'693'403'575'262.4 US$ and in EC was 108'108'009'000 US$ [3].
Sources: 
[1] "Non-refractory clay roofing tiles", EUROPEAN UNION (28), PRODQNT.
Industry, trade and services&gt;Statistics on the production of manufactured foods (prom)&gt;Sold production, exports and imports (ds-056120). Retrieved from: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/DS-056120__custom_7772056/default/table?lang=en
[2] ecoinvent v2 Report 7, Buildings, Part IV, p. 25. Presumed weight per tile: 4 kg.
[3] https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD
</productionVolumeComment>
