        <unitName xml:lang="en">m3</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. Evaporated water is produced during two processes: 1) Combustion process, where water in wet mass amount in the wood chips gets evaporated (calculated as wood_fuel*water_in_wet_mass/1000); and 2) Drying process of the roof tiles (weight of a just made tile and a fired tile are considered).</comment>
